summary: Thank you SKAM France for this amazing saison 3. It has been full of highs and lows, laughter and tears, heartbreak and love....
body: Thank you SKAM France for this amazing saison 3. It has been full of highs and lows, laughter and tears, heartbreak and love. Thank you Lucas for this look into a few months of your life. You’ve come so far, and I’m so happy for you. I hope you’ll future will be bright. It will be hard to let you go, but at the same time it will be interesting to get a look into Imane’s life, to follow her journey. And after all, we’re not letting Lucas and Eliott go. They’ll still be there, just in the background, being happy and without drama, just like they deserve. This season brought me so much joy, and I can’t really believe it’s over. It was beautiful, really. T’es pas comme les autres, saison 3. See you tomorrow (or rather today) for saison 4 mes mecs. And remember: l’amour gagne toujours ❤️

summary:
If I had to pick a favorite moment across all Evak universes, it has to be the almost kiss at the end of episode three.
Even &...
body:
If I had to pick a favorite moment across all Evak universes, it has to be the almost kiss at the end of episode three.

Even & Isak showed so much raw magnetism, and so much insecurity at the same time. I’ve legit watched that almost kiss 100s of times and it’s probably my favorite scenes in the show.

Marti & Nico had a completely different vibe. They were happy, playful. Not as much passion there (more than made up for that in the first kiss), but that pinky graze was electric.

Eliott & Lucas never even leaned in but the chemistry was so strong, the desire so strong, Ive watched it over and over. I love the way they were challenging each other, both so bold and beautiful. One my favorite scenes in the series.

Matteo & David gave off almost the same vibes as Isak and Even, the unbelievable energy coursing through the room, the slightly awkward insecurity… My skin sizzled when their lips touched for that fraction of a second.

Very much looking forward to a moment like this between Cris & Joana!

I love when characters have a chance to breathe into their attraction, when they are forced to endure the presence of the other without being able to touch them the way they want. Basically, I love torture, and Skam serves me well.

summary: I can’t even begin to express what Lucas’ story has meant to me. Being on this journey with him, watching him learn to be his...
body:
I can’t even begin to express what Lucas’ story has meant to me. Being on this journey with him, watching him learn to be his true self, witnessing him fall in love with someone who has taught him so much, seeing him happy in his own skin..it has truly changed me in the deepest way. No character -no show- has ever affected me quite like this. I am truly grateful to have been a part of it and I know this one will stay with me for a long time.

I am especially grateful we haven’t seen the last of Lucas and I look forward to seeing his story continue through Imane’s eyes. And hopefully through many other eyes as well. What a journey we’ve all been on.❤️
